== Serivisi ==
VugaPay ni serivisi yo kwambukiranya imipaka ituma ubucuruzi n'abakoresha bahinduranya amafaranga muri sisitemu nkuru yo kwishyura. Ikurikiza uburyo bwubucuruzi busa nka PayPal . VugaPay yisobanura nk'umufuka wa digitale. Abayikoresha biyandikisha kandi bashiraho konti batanga amakuru yibanze namakuru ya konte ya banki ukoresheje porogaramu zabo zigendanwa, USSD kuri terefone ziranga cyangwa kurubuga rwa VugaPay bashobora kubona abandi bakoze konti. Inshuti n'abakira ibikorwa mushobora kubibona mukoresheje nimero ya terefone, izina rya VugaPay, cyangwa imeri.<ref>https://ktpress.rw/2017/05/how-rwandan-college-brothers-coded-their-way-to-silicon-valley/</ref><ref>https://ktpress.rw/2017/05/how-rwandan-college-brothers-coded-their-way-to-silicon-valley/</ref><ref>https://ktpress.rw/2017/05/how-rwandan-college-brothers-coded-their-way-to-silicon-valley/</ref>

